1.Running as live-demo with pkg included. 
  need demokey input to active full feature.
  or with limited CPU/Storage.
  auto-reboot after running 2 days.
  choosing demo feature set.

2.Can be used as installation CD
  will geneate a uuid as register key.
  key is global unique.
  need a request file send to server
  response text file as license data
  newlicense and updatelicense is different!

3.Can be used as rescue CD
  1. fixe grub
  2. check && fixe files: kernel, bootconfig, pkgchecksum etc.
  3. grab setting and log
  4. backup setting log, user data license etc.
  5. restore backup archives
  6. create USB boot disk

